    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## INPUT FIELDS\n\n`action`: `get|upsert|delete`\n- example: `get`\n`tableName`: ten Data Table can doc/ghi\n- example: `Book Review Sessions`\n`keyField`: logical key name\n- example: `sessionToken`\n`keyValue`: logical key value\n- example: `review_abc123`\n`data`: object payload cho `upsert`\n- example: `{ \"sessionToken\": \"review_abc123\", \"status\": \"reviewing\" }`\n\n### Quick examples\n`get` -> `{ action: \"get\", tableName: \"Book Review Sessions\", keyField: \"sessionToken\", keyValue: \"review_abc123\", data: {} }`\n`upsert` -> `{ action: \"upsert\", tableName: \"Book Review Sessions\", keyField: \"sessionToken\", keyValue: \"review_abc123\", data: { sessionToken: \"review_abc123\", status: \"reviewing\" } }`\n`delete` -> `{ action: \"delete\", tableName: \"Book Review Sessions\", keyField: \"sessionToken\", keyValue: \"review_abc123\", data: {} }`\n\n### Output\n`status`, `found`, `row`",
        "height": 760,
        "width": 760,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "dt-note-1",
      "name": "NOTE::DATATABLESTORE::INPUT_FIELDS",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
